<pb ed="T" id="T19.0948.0189a" n="0189a"/>
<lb n="0189a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0189a02"/><head type="no">No. 948</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0189a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0189001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十七帖，【乙】仁和寺藏古寫本，【丙】嘉保二年寫仁和寺藏本</note>金輪王佛頂要略念誦<note n="0189002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（通諸佛頂）細註【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189002"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">法<note place="inline">通諸佛頂</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0189a04"/>
<lb n="0189a05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0189003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開府…寺〕三十七字【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府…寺〕三十七字<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">－</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189003" word-count="37"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0189a06"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空謚大鑒
<lb n="0189a07"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0189004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（唐北天竺）＋三【明】，（大興善寺）＋三【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189004"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺三</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三</rdg></app>藏沙<note n="0189005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189005"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a08"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0189a09"/><p>諸供養儀軌。如<note n="0189006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餘＝來【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189006"><lem>餘</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">來</rdg></app>經中廣說。今但晨暮修
<lb n="0189a10"/>行。或四時三時常習不間故。略去重疊簡其
<lb n="0189a11"/>要略。行者欲作諸佛頂念誦。先結三部心印
<lb n="0189a12"/>及誦真言。加持三業。佛部心印。二手右押左
<lb n="0189a13"/>內相叉。二輪並&CB00594;真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a14"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0189007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）細註【明】＊</note><app n="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>爾<note place="inline"><note n="0189008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈＝惹【明】</note><app n="0189008"><lem>慈</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">惹</rdg></app>以<note n="0189009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】</note><app n="0189009"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>下同</note>曩<note n="0189010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝&CB00768;【明】【甲】</note><app n="0189010"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00768;</rdg></app>翼<note place="inline"><note n="0189011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＝二合【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189011"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">二合</rdg></app></note>迦<note place="inline">半<note n="0189012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＋（二）【明】＊</note><app n="0189012"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a15"/><p>次結蓮華部心印。即前印以左輪屈入掌真
<lb n="0189a16"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a17"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline"><note n="0189013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>嚕<note place="inline">轉舌引</note>力迦<note place="inline">半<app type="＊" source="0189012"><lem>音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a18"/><p>次結金剛部心印。即前佛部心印。屈右輪入
<lb n="0189a19"/>掌真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a20"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0189014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189014"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">半<app type="＊" source="0189012"><lem>音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a21"/><p>次結如來拳印。<note n="0189015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189015"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>手蓋光高勝四指。握拳&CB00594;
<lb n="0189a22"/>左輪。右手作金剛拳。握左輪甲真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189a23"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>僕<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0189016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欠＋（二）細註【明】，欠入＝入欠【丙】</note><note n="0189016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欠入＝入欠【丙】，欠＋（二）細註【明】</note><app n="0189016"><lem>欠入</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">入欠</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">欠<note place="inline">二</note>入</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉吽<note place="inline">引胸喉中<note n="0189017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＝音【乙】</note><app n="0189017"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app>如牛<note n="0189018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吼＋（三）【明】</note><app n="0189018"><lem>吼</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">吼三</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a24"/><p>隨誦真言。以印加持自身五處。身器清淨與
<lb n="0189a25"/>法相應。便以印加持道場中地。誦真言七遍。
<lb n="0189a26"/>其處變成金剛界宮。自然而有眾寶。嚴飾如
<lb n="0189a27"/>佛淨土</p>
<lb n="0189a28"/><p>次結被金剛甲冑護身印。即前佛部心印。二
<lb n="0189a29"/>光直&CB00594;頭相拄。屈上節如劍<note n="0189019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔形〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189019"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。二蓋各附二
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0948.0189b" n="0189b"/>
<lb n="0189b01"/>光背。勿相著。以印加持額上右肩左肩心喉
<lb n="0189b02"/>五處。各誦一遍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189b03"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0189020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（引）＋一【明】，〔一〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189020"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>斫羯囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0189021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【丙】</note><app n="0189021"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">合引</rdg></app></note>&CB02594;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二<note n="0189022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（二）【明】，（一）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189022"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">合二</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">合一</rdg></app></note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0189b04"/>捨弭多<note place="inline"><note n="0189023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【明】</note><app n="0189023"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app></note>囉捺囉<note place="inline"><note n="0189024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="0189024"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>合引</note><note n="0189025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔囉捺囉二合引三〕－【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189025"><lem>囉捺囉<note place="inline"><note n="0189026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合引三＝三合引【乙】</note><app n="0189026"><lem>二合引<note n="0189027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【明】</note><app n="0189027"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">三合引</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>跋娑
<lb n="0189b05"/>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>攃<note place="inline">倉<note n="0189028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辣反＝葛切【明】</note><app n="0189028"><lem>辣反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">葛切</rdg></app></note><note n="0189029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">路＋（引）細註【甲】【乙】，路＝跛【丙】</note><app n="0189029"><lem>路</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">路<note place="inline">引</note></rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">跛</rdg></app>瑟抳<note n="0189030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【丙】＊</note><app n="0189030"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>灑<note place="inline"><note n="0189031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝五【明】＊</note><note n="0189031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>四＝五【明】＊</note><app n="0189031"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note>囉乞灑<app type="＊" source="0189030"><lem><note place="inline">二
<lb n="0189b06"/>合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引<note n="0189032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＝六【明】</note><app n="0189032"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">六</rdg></app></note>吽<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0189033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發＝撥（普&CB00425;反）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189033"><lem>發</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">撥（普&CB00425;反）</rdg></app>吒<note place="inline"><note n="0189034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上普&CB00425;反下吒〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189034"><lem>上普&CB00425;反下吒</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>半音</note>娑
<lb n="0189b07"/>&CB00085;<note n="0189035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合引〕－【明】</note><app n="0189035"><lem><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>賀<note place="inline">引<note n="0189036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＝七【明】</note><app n="0189036"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">七</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189b08"/><p>次結迎請聖眾印。二手仰相叉。以二蓋頭相
<lb n="0189b09"/>拄如<note n="0189037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（蓮）＋車【丙】</note><app n="0189037"><lem>車</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">蓮車</rdg></app>輅。隨誦真言。以二輪各撥二光。向
<lb n="0189b10"/>身招之或三或七。想諸聖眾乘此車輅來降
<lb n="0189b11"/>道場。迎請真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189b12"/><p type="dharani">娜麼娑怛&CB00942;<note place="inline">三合轉舌<note n="0189038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝呼【丙】</note><app n="0189038"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">呼</rdg></app></note>野<note place="inline">一</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦南<note place="inline">二</note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0189b13"/>怛他<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>&CB00344;跢<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">三</note><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0189039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0189039"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">合引</rdg></app></note>儗<note place="inline">霓以<note n="0189040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】＊</note><app n="0189040"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0189b14"/>孃<note place="inline">四</note>羯囉灑<note place="inline">二合</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0189041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引五〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189041"><lem><note place="inline">引五</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b15"/><p>次結辦事佛頂印。辟除結界。即前佛部心印。
<lb n="0189b16"/>直&CB00594;二光頭相柱。屈上節如<note n="0189042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉤＝&CB00582;【明】，&CB01894;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉤＝&CB00582;【明】，＝&CB01894;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189042"><lem>鉤</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00582;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB01894;</rdg></app>。隨誦真言以
<lb n="0189b17"/>印頂上左轉三匝。辟除一切不祥諸作障者。
<lb n="0189b18"/>便右旋三匝。即成結界辦事真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189b19"/><p type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note>唵吒嚕唵<note place="inline"><note n="0189043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="0189043"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0189039"><lem>合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0189b20"/>滿馱娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0189044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189044"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0189045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（三）【明】，〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189045"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引三</note></rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b21"/><p>次結大三昧耶印即前被甲印二。蓋稍開如
<lb n="0189b22"/>杵形。以二輪各附二蓋下第一文真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189b23"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>餉<note place="inline">商障<app type="＊" source="0189040"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>迦<note n="0189046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隸＝&CB00942;【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0189046" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB00619;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">隸</rdg></app>＝&CB00942;【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0189046"><lem>&CB00619;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00942;</rdg></app><note place="inline">轉舌<note n="0189047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝二【明】，〔一〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189047"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">鼻<note n="0189048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔音〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189048"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>閻
<lb n="0189b24"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0189049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引三）細註【明】，（引二）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0189049"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引三</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b25"/><p>隨誦真言。以印准前右旋三匝。隨行人意遠
<lb n="0189b26"/>近。結為大界</p>
<lb n="0189b27"/><p>次結部母佛眼尊印。二手合掌以二蓋各捻
<lb n="0189b28"/>二光背。令如眼<note n="0189050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝刑【甲】</note><app n="0189050"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">刑</rdg></app>。雙屈二輪入掌真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0948.0189c" n="0189c"/>
