<lb n="0189c05"/><p>次結本尊頂輪王印。即前辦事佛頂印。以二
<lb n="0189c06"/>輪並&CB00594;。二蓋平屈兩節頭相<note n="0189060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189060"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>。於二輪甲
<lb n="0189c07"/>上。結印當心誦真言七遍或一百八遍。又加
<lb n="0189c08"/>持身五處各一遍。加持力故。身與本尊合為
<lb n="0189c09"/>一體。一字輪王陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0189c10"/><p type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note n="0189061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">南＋（一）細註【明】</note><app n="0189061"><lem>南</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">南<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>勃嚕唵<note place="inline">三<app type="＊" source="0189039"><lem>合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">合引</rdg></app>嚕字彈舌為一音又引
<lb n="0189c11"/>聲從胸喉中出其音如擊大鼓古譯云步林者訛略不正也</note></p>
<lb n="0189c12"/><p>次結獻閼伽<note n="0189062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔香〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189062"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>水印。即前大三昧耶印。以二
<lb n="0189c13"/>蓋附著二光背。二輪又安二蓋<note n="0189063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔側〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189063"><lem>側</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>下第一文。
<lb n="0189c14"/>如商佉羸盃形。心想印中滿盛香水。舉印額
<lb n="0189c15"/>齊。奉獻香水。澡浴本尊及諸聖眾真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189c16"/><p type="dharani">娜莫<note n="0189064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＋（去）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189064"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">三<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app>滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note><app type="＊" source="0189007"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>遏<note place="inline">轉舌</note>伽<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>囉
