<lb n="0190a18"/>合</note>&CB00085;<note n="0190015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乃〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190015"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">鼻<note n="0190016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＋（引）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0190016"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">音引</rdg></app></note><note n="0190017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迦＋（二）細註【明】</note><app n="0190017"><lem>迦</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">迦<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>滿<note place="inline">引</note>馱吠<note n="0190018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔敷閉反二〕－【明】，敷＝微【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190018"><lem><note place="inline">敷閉反<note n="0190019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190019"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">微閉反二</note></rdg></app>三<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0189013"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline"><note n="0190020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鼻＋（音）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0190020"><lem>鼻</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">鼻音</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0190a19"/>娑多<note place="inline">二合</note>尾&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0190a07"/>引</note>地跛作訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline"><note n="0190021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鼻＋（音）【丙】</note><app n="0190021"><lem>鼻</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">鼻音</rdg></app>引</note>
<lb n="0190a20"/>里寧<note n="0190022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190022"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曩謨娑&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝怛囉<note n="0190023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190023"><lem><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>怛哩作訖
<lb n="0190a21"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>底<note n="0190024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔丁以反〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190024"><lem><note place="inline">丁以反</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>寧<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0190a22"/><p>每念誦先。以五支。或以五相八<note n="0190025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190025"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>等觀智。
<lb n="0190a23"/>成本尊瑜伽<note place="inline">此法並在頂輪瑜伽極深密一一皆<note n="0190026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔須〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190026"><lem>須</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>從灌頂阿闍<note n="0190027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梨＝黎【明】</note><app n="0190027"><lem>梨</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">黎</rdg></app>親<note n="0190028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【明】，受＋（之）【丙】</note><app n="0190028"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">受之</rdg></app></note>或於
<lb n="0190a24"/>自身。想布一字安三處<note place="inline">頂舌<note n="0190029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＋（也）【丙】</note><app n="0190029"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">心也</rdg></app></note>以字威力能成
<lb n="0190a25"/>佛頂輪王尊。又想曼茶<note n="0190030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＝囉【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190030"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>中有香水大海。於
<lb n="0190a26"/>海中心有妙高山。七重金山<note n="0190031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">周＝週【明】</note><app n="0190031"><lem>周</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">週</rdg></app>匝圍遶。於妙
<lb n="0190a27"/>高頂上有八葉白色蓮華。於一一葉上。右旋
<lb n="0190a28"/>布列輪王七寶。所謂金輪象馬珠女兵及主
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0948.0190b" n="0190b"/>
<lb n="0190b01"/>藏。當前第八葉。想安佛眼尊。十佛頂眷屬前
<lb n="0190b02"/>後圍遶。先住此觀已。然後持珠相應念誦。或
<lb n="0190b03"/>百或千或至於萬。常功限畢。捧珠頂戴誦部
<lb n="0190b04"/>母尊。所有功業願尊守護。又結根本印加身
<lb n="0190b05"/>五處。又結普供養印如前供養。又以悅<note n="0190032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00540;＝喜心【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190032"><lem>&CB00540;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">喜心</rdg></app>歌
<lb n="0190b06"/>讚本尊。無量悲願攝護我等。令得解脫悉地
<lb n="0190b07"/>相應。廣發弘願利樂有情<note n="0190033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔誓〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190033"><lem>誓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>成正覺。次捧閼
<lb n="0190b08"/>伽如前奉獻。又結辦事佛頂印。左旋解界。又
<lb n="0190b09"/>結前迎請印。向外撥二中指。誦前真言去羯
<lb n="0190b10"/><note n="0190034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0190034"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>灑野句。應云尾薩惹野。即成奉送。又結
<lb n="0190b11"/>被甲印誦前真言加身五處。又結三部心印。
<lb n="0190b12"/><note n="0190035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虔＝處【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0190035"><lem>虔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>誠作禮發願。<note n="0190036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">任＝往【明】</note><app n="0190036"><lem>任</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">往</rdg></app>出道場或旋繞經行。轉
<lb n="0190b13"/>讀大乘經典。作諸善業以助成就</p>
<lb n="0190b14"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0190037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一字）＋金【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190037"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">一字金</rdg></app>輪王佛頂要略念誦<note n="0190038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（終）細註【明】，乙本奧書曰保安二年孟夏以證本比校了，丙本卷末曰持智手大印處於師子座日輪日蓮臺智拳印所謂金剛拳及成右掘左頭指一節面當心是名智拳印當誦此密言勃魯唵，丙本奧書曰嘉保二年四月二十日於金剛&CB00123;寺奧院書之執筆淳譽</note><app n="0190038"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">法<note place="inline">終</note></rdg></app><note n="0190038" place="foot" type="rest">乙本奧書曰保安二年孟夏以證本比校了，丙本卷末曰持智手大印處於師子座日輪日蓮臺智拳印所謂金剛拳及成右掘左頭指一節面當心是名智拳印當誦此密言勃魯唵，丙本奧書曰嘉保二年四月二十日於金剛&CB00123;寺奧院書之執筆淳譽</note></jhead></juan></div1>
